|Re(z)|, |Im(z)| \leq |z|
z=a+bi
(|a|,|b|) \leq |a+bi|
(a,b) \leq \sqrt{a^2+b^2} 
(a+bi) \leq \sqrt{a^2+b^2} 
a^2 +2abi -b^2 \leq a^2 + b^2
ai \leq b
Re(z)=\frac{z+\bar z}{2}\implies|Re(z)|=|\frac{z+\bar z}{2}|\iff |Re(z)|=|\dfrac z2 + \frac{\bar z}{2}| \le \dfrac 12|z|+\dfrac 12|\bar z|
|\bar z| = |z|
|Re(z)| \le \dfrac 12|z| + \dfrac 12|z| = |z|
|Im(z)|,
Im(z)=\frac{z-\bar z}{2i}
